elements.text: It just mostly proves things to do with optimizations

text:
```julia> using StaticArrays

julia> function f(v::AbstractVector)
           if length(v) < 10
               1
           else
               2
           end
       end
f (generic function with 1 method)

julia> code_typed(f, (SVector{3},))
1-element Vector{Any}:
 CodeInfo(
1 ─     Main.length(v)::Core.Const(3)
└──     return 1
) => Int64```
